column5: Got out this evening around 7:00, searched around a bit and then at 7:30 got my first bite of the evening, 30 inch pike. In the next hour I landed 6 pike, 5 were around 30" and one was real nice 36"er. I also lost 2 more at the side of the boat and had a larger one follow. Certainly my best hour of pike fishing. Can't wait to get back out there and get another one over 40.
nothing like a quick outing with a high score ; nice
sweet pike, good way to remember the OFC sign too by keepin it in the wallet
Now thats an average for an hour!  Congrats
Great way to spend an evening & hopefully you do catch a 40+ Tight Lines SBK
sweet pike, maybe one day I'll do as good as that!
